HEADWORD: Exarch
<hw>Ex"arch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exarchus</ets>, Gr. <?/ <?/ commander; <?/,<?/, out + <?/ to lead,
rule: cf. F. <ets>exarque</ets>.]</ety> <def>A viceroy; in Ravenna, the
title of the viceroys of the Byzantine emperors; in the Eastern Church,
